{"tid":2038192,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★港交所(00388)已沒收未領取的2013年度末期息共1002萬元","createTime":"2020-05-27T11:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T14:29:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7b8976ce12e5b90eb44a42f2dcc8358be080c5","tid":2038192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"&lt;匯港通訊&gt; 港交所(00388)於2020年4月9日宣布，根據香港交易所《組織章程細則》，於2014 年5月27日派付而於 2020年5月27日仍為未領取的2013年度末期股息每股 1.72 元將予沒收及復歸香港交易所。因此，仍未被領取的 2013 年度末期股息合共 1002.8361萬元已於今天被沒收並復歸香港交易所。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80-00388-%E5%B7%B2%E6%B2%92%E6%94%B6%E6%9C%AA%E9%A0%98%E5%8F%96%E7%9A%842013%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%AB%E6%9C%9F%E6%81%AF%E5%85%B11002%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-093708297.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2589%2580-00388-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%2594%25B6%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%259A%25842013%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%2581%25AF%25E5%2585%25B11002%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583-093708297.html&d=YPabaHIeuUhgFn7y0hV32Sukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=6916f672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80-00388-%E5%B7%B2%E6%B2%92%E6%94%B6%E6%9C%AA%E9%A0%98%E5%8F%96%E7%9A%842013%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%AB%E6%9C%9F%E6%81%AF%E5%85%B11002%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-093708297.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n＃5股東很想要吧！"},{"pid":"06ccd9c0d6aeb99a74e536ef7c26694caadf29f6","tid":2038192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"＃5股東很想要吧！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},